# ManagedBackgroundAssetsError.fileNotFound(at:)

**Case**

An error that’s thrown when the system can’t find a file at the specified path.

## Declaration

```swift
case fileNotFound(at: FilePath)
```

## Errors

- **ManagedBackgroundAssetsError.assetPackNotFound(withID:)**: An error that’s thrown when the system can’t find an asset pack with the given ID.
